State.Author: monobelisk
State.Description: Make Skyrim look like a mid-90's DOS game. A tweakable ENB post-processing effect that emulates a retro look by using pixelation, posterization/palette color mapping and ordered dithering. As a finishing touch, this effect emulates an old-school CRT monitor by using a screen curve effect, combined with scanlines and vignette.
State.Name: Retro Skyrim
